If you use \Rfunction{oncoSimulPop} the arguments for
\texttt{detectionSize}, \texttt{detectionDrivers} must be the same for all
simulations. This is not the case for \Rfunction{oncoSimulSample}.


\Rfunction{samplePop} can only sample with the arguments you give
